item.dc:creator: @Graham Graham
item.description:
@Graham wrote:

You have to open the JAVA files, not the CLASS ones. It makes it easier if you view file extensions (the java files end in .java, whereas the class files end in .class). Go to Tools -> Folder Options -> View and untick “Hide extensions for known file types”.

Then you should be able to see and open the correct files.
